name: 7MinScoreCollect
description:
WASD to move, you can collect Godot logos and you get one score for each one you pick up, what more is there to expect in 7 minutes ;)

Made the game in 7 minutes (and 54 seconds) excluding the time uploading the game on itch. I couldn't upload a youtube video but if you want a proof of that I made the game in 7 mins i added a mp4 video to be downloaded.
